    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and discover the map and its areas, picking up items and solving various puzzles on your way to the flag ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This new take on the Metroidvania genre is sure to surprise you, using a grid system which allows you to place and pick up items all around the map to help you solve various kinds of puzzles in a relaxing, no rush environment ! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SIMPLE GAMEPLAY FEATURES ! </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2D platformer with side scrolling</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grid system to place/pick up items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Range of puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-save and Load</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Best of luck on your way to the flag!</p>",
